---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { BorderBeam } from '@/components/magicui/border-beam'

import izzaPhoto from '../assets/izza.jpeg';
---

<Layout 
  title="About | Yusril Izza Aulia"
  description="Learn more about Yusril Izza Aulia - a Fullstack Engineer specializing in React, Next.js, Remix, Svelte, Node.js, and Golang development."
>
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="flex-1">
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-12 md:mb-20">About Me</h1>
        
        <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-16">
          <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-8 text-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed text-pretty">
            <p>
              <strong class="text-foreground font-semibold">Hello! I'm Yusril Izza Aulia</strong>, a results-driven Fullstack Engineer with 5+ years of experience building scalable web applications using React, Node.js, and TypeScript. I have a proven track record of leading frontend teams, optimizing application performance, and delivering end-to-end solutions for enterprise clients.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              My journey in tech began with a JavaScript Fullstack Bootcamp at Dumbways in 2019, which laid the foundation for my career. Since then, I've worked with companies like Qonflo AI, where I architected a high-performance workflow orchestration engine; Ultravoucher, where I led frontend development for the Central Reporting Platform; and PT. Software Service Indonesia, where I developed solutions for international clients including Agentpoint and Evergen Australia.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              I'm passionate about clean code, developer experience, and modern JavaScript ecosystems. My expertise extends to workflow orchestration, AI integration, and real-time data synchronization systems. Outside of my professional work, I enjoy building personal SaaS products and open-source tools, exploring full product lifecycles from ideation to deployment.
            </p>
            
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground mt-16 mb-8">Core Values</h2>
            
            <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 text-base">
              <div class="relative overflow-hidden p-6 rounded-3xl bg-neutral-50/50 dark:bg-neutral-900/50 border border-neutral-200/50 dark:border-neutral-800/50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Performance-Focused</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">Dedicated to creating high-performance web applications with optimized load times and smooth user experiences.</p>
                <BorderBeam client:idle duration={8} size={100} />
              </div>
              
              <div class="relative overflow-hidden p-6 rounded-3xl bg-neutral-50/50 dark:bg-neutral-900/50 border border-neutral-200/50 dark:border-neutral-800/50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground mb-2">User-Centric Design</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">Prioritizing intuitive interfaces that solve real problems for users while maintaining elegant, minimalist design principles.</p>
                <BorderBeam client:idle duration={8} size={100} />
              </div>
              
              <div class="relative overflow-hidden p-6 rounded-3xl bg-neutral-50/50 dark:bg-neutral-900/50 border border-neutral-200/50 dark:border-neutral-800/50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"></path><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Continuous Learning</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">Always expanding my knowledge in emerging technologies like Generative AI and RAG to stay at the forefront of the industry.</p>
                <BorderBeam client:idle duration={8} size={100} />
              </div>
              
              <div class="relative overflow-hidden p-6 rounded-3xl bg-neutral-50/50 dark:bg-neutral-900/50 border border-neutral-200/50 dark:border-neutral-800/50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Technical Excellence</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">Committed to writing clean, maintainable code with comprehensive testing and documentation for long-term project success.</p>
                <BorderBeam client:idle duration={8} size={100} />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="md:col-span-4">
            <div class="sticky top-24">
              <div class="relative w-full aspect-square rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden mb-8 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 shadow-xl shadow-neutral-200/50 dark:shadow-none">
                <Image src={izzaPhoto} alt="Muhamad Yusril Izza Aulia" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
              
              <div class="p-6 rounded-[2rem] bg-neutral-50/50 dark:bg-neutral-900/50 border border-neutral-200/50 dark:border-neutral-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">Quick Facts</h2>
                
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                  <li class="flex flex-col gap-1 pb-4 border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Location</span>
                    <span class="font-medium text-foreground">Yogyakarta, Indonesia</span>
                  </li>
                  
                  <li class="flex flex-col gap-1 pb-4 border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Education</span>
                    <span class="font-medium text-foreground">B.S. Informatics Engineering<br/><span class="text-sm font-normal text-neutral-500">Asia Cyber University</span></span>
                  </li>
                  
                  <li class="flex flex-col gap-1 pb-4 border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Languages</span>
                    <span class="font-medium text-foreground">Indonesian, English</span>
                  </li>
                  
                  <li class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Current Focus</span>
                    <span class="font-medium text-foreground leading-snug">Workflow Orchestration, AI Integration, Developer Experience, Fullstack Engineering</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
